name: BizDAO
description:
Business oriented Metaverse:

Imagine that you invest cryptoassets in real
businesses and become a member of BizDAO -
Business Decentralized Autonomous Organization.
Now you have your own virtual office and you take
a part in key decisions related to business that you
are interested in.
It's like monopoly with the one exeption.
The players are not competitors.
They are associates.
Propose and vote for all business decisions
together to run the business profitable.
